                    <comment id="12591760" author="mikemccand" created="Wed, 23 Apr 2008 20:52:36 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This changes the segments file to store the deletion count per&lt;br/&gt;
segment. I added package-private get/setDelCount to SegmentInfo.  I&lt;br/&gt;
also added BitVector.getAndSet, which sets the bit but returns the&lt;br/&gt;
starting value of that bit. I use this to only increment deletion&lt;br/&gt;
count if the doc wasn&apos;t already deleted.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I plan to commit in a day or two.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
